## Framework-Specific Patterns

### Web Frontend

**React:** Functional with hooks, useState/useReducer, useMemo/useCallback, Error boundaries
**Vue:** Composition API, Composables, Pinia stores, Named slots
**Angular:** Standalone components, Injectable services, RxJS + Signals, Reactive forms
**Next.js:** App Router, Server components, Route handlers, revalidate + cache tags

### Web Backend

**Node.js:** Controllers + services + repos, async/await, Zod/Joi, Prisma/TypeORM
**Python:** Type hints, asyncio, Pydantic, pytest fixtures
**Laravel:** Single responsibility controllers, Eloquent scopes, Form requests, Events
**Go:** cmd/internal/pkg structure, Explicit errors, Interfaces, Table-driven tests

### Mobile

**React Native:** React Navigation v6+, NativeWind/StyleSheet, Zustand, Detox
**Flutter:** Widget composition, Riverpod/BLoC, go_router, Platform channels

### Game

**Godot:** Scene composition, GDScript with static typing, Custom signals, Multi-platform export

